    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Larry Robinson divided his team into three groups to open camp in West Orange, N.J. Two groups scrimmaged in the morning and the third practiced drills in the afternoon.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Larry Robinson divided his team into three groups to open camp in West Orange, N.J. Two groups scrimmaged in the morning and the third practiced drills in the afternoon.</p>
        <p>Missing were Jason Arnott and Scott Niedermayer, who are unsigned restricted free agents, and Petr Sykora, who had emergency surgery Thursday night to have his tonsils removed.</p>
        <p>Sykora will miss at least a week of camp.</p>
        <p>Alex Yannis</p>
        <p>PLUS: HOCKEY</p>
